{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if we'd look out my window, we'd have a real nice view of prisons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but only for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I pointed out to you that you had to have this ironclad nervous control and assurance that under no circumstance were we ever gonna be in doubt about a word.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now you've heard me two, three times grope for a name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, you can't do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to have it boom, boom, boom, boom, instantly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I became very aware very quickly that I did not have this iron nervous assurance, ironclad nervous assurance that I would never do that, you see.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I-- I did it once or twice just to be able to say I had done it, but no, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I purposely did not put myself in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Jesus.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had these-- we had, first of all, Army jeeps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we-- we took over from the German army certain vehicles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from-- from the German army, I got a-- an Opel sedan, about 1937 or '38 model.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I tell you, it was in terrible condition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I claimed it had gone to-- to-- to Stalingrad and back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every time you'd run it up a hill, it'd catch fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you'd sit down, and there was a spring that would hit you in the bottom of the you-know-what.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And oh, and so when Wallie Cohn came into the picture-- I told you about Wallie, didn't I?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well anyway, he appeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
